src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本個制度有問題<br />\n政府班垃圾官個個都食塞米</blockquote><br />\n97之後班公務官由下至上真係一代不如一代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577f02b60eb392b3dbef447e0a1798871a6b1611","tid":187423,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"首先點定義「港人」先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063ad49272165fb4b6182ca050561bb9edc2ee9","tid":187423,"uid":102749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2人家庭都幾難唔過3萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗出黎果個都冇撚腦<br />\n依家最大問題就係一班搵緊15000-25000既人上唔撚到車<br />\n冇屋企人幫首期真係食撚屎<br />\n抽居屋仲難過中六合彩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家抽居屋個規制太on9，綠白一齊抽到底係邊個諗出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直頭分做兩樣野啦<br />\n綠置居 + 居屋(淨係比依家白表既人抽)<br />\n用得綠表姐係有得住啦<br />\n白表既人好明顯係急過綠表</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n綠表班人大部份真係「揀樓」，之前都訪問過有唔少人揀唔啱索性唔買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本個制度有問題<br />\n政府班垃圾官個個都食塞米</blockquote><br />\n個公屋富戶政策一早要出黎啦<br />\n有乜理由叫納稅人養有班錢人住公屋<br />\n<br />\n689個仆街心懷不軌<br />\n出左咁多辣招,趕盡左好多需求<br />\n用呢招黎迫d人買樓,托住個市<br />\n<br />\n呢個政策係好,但係諗出黎果個人係立心不良<br />\n根本唔係幫緊人置業"},{"pid":"a1988a552fe87de15e95328d7865a6dc40a4a5dc","tid":187423,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>限呎有撚用咩, 限價啦<img src=\"/a